* [[礼]] - '''Rei''' - [[respect]]
* [[誠]] - '''Makoto''' - [[honesty]]
* [[名誉]] - '''Meiyo''' - [[honour]]
* [[忠義]] - '''Chugi''' - [[loyalty]]
